net.proteusframework.data.filesystem.http

Class FileEntityImageResourceFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.proteusframework.data.filesystem.http.FileEntityImageResourceFactory
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    net.proteusframework.internet.http.resource.ResourceFactory

    @Service
public class FileEntityImageResourceFactory
extends Object
implements net.proteusframework.internet.http.resource.ResourceFactory
    Resource factory for images stored as file entities that can be served in arbitrary dimensions. The width or height may be less than or equal to zero to preserve the aspect ratio and adjust that argument as needed.
    Author:
    Pat B. Double (double@i2rd.com)
